impact on government,

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:24.270
both here in the UK, in the
US, and elsewhere, which

00:00:24.270 --> 00:00:26.710
is the successes that we've
seen over the last few years

00:00:26.710 --> 00:00:29.270
around opening the data
that government holds.

