a range of things

00:30:22.720 --> 00:30:26.584
from giving of one's
time, sharing information,

00:30:26.584 --> 00:30:28.000
to actually building
the platforms

00:30:28.000 --> 00:30:29.958
and tech to enable other
people to participate.

